00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:43,620
You told me that you loved Din like your own brother

505
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:46,347
and that you would do anything for him.

506
00:32:46,347 --> 00:32:47,602
Yes.

507
00:32:47,602 --> 00:32:51,453
Could you do something for Din this time?

508
00:32:53,860 --> 00:32:58,306
Ms. Chairwoman, what do you want me to do?

509
00:32:58,306 --> 00:33:02,160
You should make Kheetika fall in love with you.

510
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:06,210
You should let Din know

511
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:10,760
how filthy and greedy she is.

512
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:15,100
When Din doesn't love her anymore, you dump her.

513
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,940
I can't lie.

514
00:33:17,940 --> 00:33:20,900
And I can't trick Kheetika.

515
00:33:20,900 --> 00:33:22,400
Why can't you do it?

516
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:25,465
Are you going to let her cheat Din and get away with it?

517
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:29,860
Could you please give me some time to think about it?

518
00:33:29,860 --> 00:33:31,500
I'll take care of it as soon as possible.

519
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:33,020
No.

520
00:33:33,020 --> 00:33:35,358
I would rather not waste any more time.

521
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:38,760
You have to follow my orders no matter what.

522
00:33:38,760 --> 00:33:41,393
But Ms. Chairwoman─

523
00:33:41,393 --> 00:33:42,780
I...

524
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:48,330
This is your chance to repay me.

525
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:50,960
I pulled you out of the trash.

526
00:33:55,020 --> 00:33:57,920
If you're ungrateful, you don't have to do it.

527
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:43,660
I'm back.

528
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:48,860
What's up, Son? What's up, Son?

529
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:26,540
Why are you so unlucky?

530
00:35:26,540 --> 00:35:29,540
Lom is getting worse.

531
00:35:30,380 --> 00:35:32,980
His fear of dirty things is affecting him.

532
00:35:32,980 --> 00:35:36,260
Look. He scratched himself and was covered in wounds.

533
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:38,760
It's really a strange disease.

534
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:40,660
I don't know what to do.

535
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:43,300
It happens every time I leave him alone at home.

536
00:35:43,300 --> 00:35:45,535
I can't bring him to work.

537
00:35:45,535 --> 00:35:48,126
Do you want to send him to the welfare home where I work?

538
00:35:48,126 --> 00:35:49,900
I'll take care of him for you.

539
00:35:49,900 --> 00:35:53,480
You can pick him up on the weekend.

540
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:57,100
But I don't have money.

541
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:59,780
You don't have to spend too much money.

542
00:35:59,780 --> 00:36:04,172
And he can study and make friends there.

543
00:36:11,540 --> 00:36:14,100
Stay with Paa Nit, Son.

544
00:36:14,100 --> 00:36:15,820
Where are you going?

545
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:17,313
I'm going to work.

546
00:36:17,313 --> 00:36:20,836
I'll pick you up on the weekend.

547
00:36:20,836 --> 00:36:23,520
I want to be with you. Don't leave me.

548
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:27,080
I won't leave you. But I have to go to work.

549
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:30,585
I promise you I'll pick you up.

550
00:36:31,680 --> 00:36:35,193
That's a deal.
- That's a deal.

551
00:36:38,860 --> 00:36:41,120
Be good here.

552
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:42,000
Remember, your mother abandoned you.

553
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:45,860
Lom was abandoned by his mother!

554
00:38:08,473 --> 00:38:09,850
Lom.

555
00:38:09,850 --> 00:38:12,573
You have a guest.

556
00:38:12,573 --> 00:38:13,954
Is it my mom?

557
00:38:13,954 --> 00:38:15,434
My mom's here.

558
00:38:15,434 --> 00:38:18,686
Mom, I'm coming.

559
00:38:27,453 --> 00:38:31,053
She's not my mother.

560
00:38:31,053 --> 00:38:35,000
Khun Premyuda will take care of you instead of your mother.

561
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:37,988
Be a good boy. Okay?

562
00:38:37,988 --> 00:38:40,560
Turn around and say hi to her.

563
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:44,525
Hello.

564
00:38:51,460 --> 00:38:54,172
This will be your home.

565
00:38:54,172 --> 00:38:59,040
You will live here as the eldest grandson of the Kukitcharoen family.

566
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:01,780
Can I see my mom?

567
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:03,866
Your mom is not here.

568
00:39:03,866 --> 00:39:06,900
And you must call me Ms. Chairwoman.

569
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:08,525
Okay.

570
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:14,480
Khun Lom.

571
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,807
I'm Paa Patthama.

572
00:39:16,807 --> 00:39:18,823
You will live with Ms. Chairwoman.

573
00:39:18,823 --> 00:39:21,486
She'll take good care of you.

574
00:39:21,486 --> 00:39:23,450
You can go to school

575
00:39:23,450 --> 00:39:27,520
and have a better life.

576
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:10,120
Isn't that too cruel, Madam?

577
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:13,500
Brothers fighting over a woman.

578
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:18,020
You won't learn your lessons

579
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:20,920
until you encounter heartbreaking things.

580
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:25,290
If your plan fails,

581
00:40:25,290 --> 00:40:28,270
Khun Din and Khun Lom...

582
00:40:28,270 --> 00:40:30,966
There will be no mistakes.

583
00:40:30,966 --> 00:40:33,333
Whether it's Din or Lom,

584
00:40:33,333 --> 00:40:35,700
I won't let Kheetika

585
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:39,600
step into my Kukitcharoen family.

586
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:42,380
I hope so.

587
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:48,220
I would rather not see you the way you were when...

588
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:51,040
you lost Khun Bonthai.

589
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:54,245
You were too impulsive.

590
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:12,280
This is your chance to repay me.

591
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:15,180
I pulled you out of the trash.

592
00:41:15,180 --> 00:41:17,820
If you're ungrateful, you don't have to do it.

593
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:29,173
Khun Sira.

594
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,993
What is it?

595
00:41:33,993 --> 00:41:36,713
I got you some breakfast.

596
00:41:36,713 --> 00:41:40,563
You left early in the morning. You must not have eaten yet.

597
00:41:40,563 --> 00:41:45,320
I got you a sandwich and a salad.

598
00:41:50,060 --> 00:41:51,992
Where have you been?

599
00:41:57,540 --> 00:41:58,968
I...

600
00:41:58,968 --> 00:42:01,800
I knew you were here.

601
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,993
Here.

602
00:42:06,220 --> 00:42:08,500
Are you going to eat breakfast?

603
00:42:08,500 --> 00:42:10,920
Good. Let's eat together.

604
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:13,460
I bought a lot of food.

605
00:42:13,460 --> 00:42:17,350
Kanghan, please get us the cutlery.

606
00:42:18,367 --> 00:42:19,973
Okay.

607
00:42:23,680 --> 00:42:25,740
Din,

608
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:28,000
my office is not a restaurant.

609
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:30,760
If you want to eat, go to the restaurant.

610
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:33,300
It's not safe to eat at the restaurant.

611
00:42:33,300 --> 00:42:35,340
It's safest to eat in your office.

612
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:37,140
What do you mean?

613
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:42,100
As you know, Grandma has many eyes in our company.

614
00:42:42,100 --> 00:42:46,600
If Kanghan and I go to a restaurant, we'll be caught.

615
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:50,400
If we eat in your office, I can say I'm here to talk about work.

616
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:53,120
You can't eat in my office.

617
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:57,280
Brother, I'm already miserable because our grandma is cruel to me.

618
00:42:57,280 --> 00:43:00,185
Don't be cruel to me.

619
00:43:00,185 --> 00:43:02,340
Don't you love me?

620
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:11,272
If I make Kanghan my girlfriend,

621
00:43:11,272 --> 00:43:14,722
I promise I won't bother you anymore. Okay?

622
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:21,700
Are you saying you're going to pursue Kanghan again?

623
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:26,250
Are you sure Kanghan still loves you?

624
00:43:26,260 --> 00:43:30,233
I'm not sure about that.

625
00:43:30,233 --> 00:43:34,810
But I'm sure you are on my side,

626
00:43:34,810 --> 00:43:36,920
and you'll help me.

627
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:39,946
What do you want me to do?

628
00:43:39,946 --> 00:43:42,960
Help me pursue Kanghan, Brother.

629
00:43:43,580 --> 00:43:46,738
Okay, Brother?

630
00:43:46,738 --> 00:43:49,138
You are the only person I trust.

631
00:43:49,138 --> 00:43:51,118
Help me.

632
00:44:00,360 --> 00:44:02,133
Thank you.

633
00:44:04,240 --> 00:44:05,920
Come on, let's go eat.

634
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:08,220
Then, I'll go out.

635
00:44:08,220 --> 00:44:11,680
Wait. Let's eat together.

636
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:13,360
Open it for me.

637
00:44:13,360 --> 00:44:14,980
Come on.

638
00:44:59,060 --> 00:45:03,140
All right, Khun Sira. Now, relax.

639
00:45:03,140 --> 00:45:07,620
And then start talking about what's bothering you.

640
00:45:07,620 --> 00:45:13,000
Doctor, if someone you love asks you for something,

641
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:18,020
but you would rather not do it, how do you say no?

642
00:45:19,660 --> 00:45:23,940
I think I'd just say no.

643
00:45:23,940 --> 00:45:27,800
But you love that person very much.

644
00:45:28,980 --> 00:45:32,820
If it's someone I love and care about,

645
00:45:32,820 --> 00:45:36,180
I might say yes.

646
00:45:41,100 --> 00:45:45,620
If I choose to help her, someone will be sad.

647
00:45:45,620 --> 00:45:47,980
Should I still help her, Doctor?

648
00:45:47,980 --> 00:45:49,470
Someone will be sad?

649
00:45:49,470 --> 00:45:52,785
If that's the case, I won't help her.

650
00:45:53,420 --> 00:45:55,552
But I love her.

651
00:45:56,180 --> 00:45:59,020
I owe her a debt.

652
00:46:00,180 --> 00:46:04,186
If I don't help her, she will be sad.

653
00:46:05,580 --> 00:46:08,620
If that's the case,

654
00:46:08,620 --> 00:46:12,360
I don't think we can find an answer.

655
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:18,160
If it's something you were asked to do, is it really so difficult to decide?

656
00:46:21,040 --> 00:46:24,946
If I help one of them,

657
00:46:26,020 --> 00:46:28,540
I will hurt the other one.

658
00:46:33,700 --> 00:46:36,660
Are you sure only one person will be sad?

659
00:46:36,660 --> 00:46:40,960
Won't you also be sad?

660
00:46:47,580 --> 00:46:49,060
Why, Kanghan?

661
00:46:49,060 --> 00:46:54,080
I just wanted to know your address. Why do you keep it a secret?

662
00:46:54,080 --> 00:46:56,624
There's no secret, Mom.

663
00:46:56,624 --> 00:46:59,410
I just don't want to disturb my friend.

664
00:46:59,410 --> 00:47:02,720
If I can't go to your apartment,

665
00:47:02,720 --> 00:47:05,034
I'll go to your company tomorrow.

666
00:47:05,034 --> 00:47:06,680
What time will you come?

667
00:47:06,680 --> 00:47:11,120
Around 11:00. I'll bring green curry for you.

668
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:14,146
Call me when you arrive.

669
00:47:14,146 --> 00:47:15,593
Hey, you.

670
00:47:15,593 --> 00:47:19,780
This garbage bag was here last night. Haven't you taken it out?

671
00:47:19,780 --> 00:47:24,310
Kanghan, I thought I heard a man's voice.

672
00:47:25,600 --> 00:47:27,860
She's not a man, Mom. She's not.

673
00:47:27,860 --> 00:47:31,900
Your hand is dirty. Your hand is so dirty.

674
00:47:31,900 --> 00:47:33,140
You.

675
00:47:33,140 --> 00:47:37,340
Kanghan, didn't you say you live with a female friend?

676
00:47:37,340 --> 00:47:40,860
He's my gay male friend, Mom.

677
00:47:40,860 --> 00:47:41,883
My gay male friend.

678
00:47:41,883 --> 00:47:43,440
My mom is on the phone.

679
00:47:43,440 --> 00:47:45,560
How am I supposed to know?

680
00:47:45,560 --> 00:47:49,400
If you don't believe me, you can talk to him.

681
00:47:49,400 --> 00:47:51,360
- Speak to her.
- What do you want me to say?

682
00:47:51,360 --> 00:47:53,340
Hello. How are you?

683
00:47:53,340 --> 00:47:54,980
Come on. Be gentle.

684
00:47:54,980 --> 00:47:57,220
I'm not a femboy. Do you want to lie to your mother? Are you crazy?

685
00:47:57,220 --> 00:47:59,520
- I don't want you to lie.
- I just─

686
00:47:59,520 --> 00:48:01,640
I just want you to parrot me.

687
00:48:01,640 --> 00:48:04,880
Come on.

688
00:48:05,860 --> 00:48:09,180
- Hello.
- Hello.

689
00:48:09,180 --> 00:48:11,191
- Come on.
- No.

690
00:48:11,191 --> 00:48:14,080
Didn't you ask me to parrot you?

691
00:48:14,080 --> 00:48:17,620
Mom, I have to go. See you tomorrow.

692
00:48:22,740 --> 00:48:24,507
What should I do?

693
00:48:24,507 --> 00:48:27,506
How do I explain it to my mom?

694
00:48:29,100 --> 00:48:31,780
You're a good liar.

695
00:48:31,780 --> 00:48:34,020
It shouldn't be hard.

696
00:48:36,500 --> 00:48:42,080
Kanghan's friend sounded familiar to me.

697
00:48:42,080 --> 00:48:44,160
What?

698
00:48:54,300 --> 00:48:56,680
It's the sound of Khun Hom's car.

699
00:48:56,680 --> 00:48:59,400
Khun Hom is here.

700
00:48:59,400 --> 00:49:02,060
Khun Hom.

701
00:49:11,100 --> 00:49:15,360
Metta, help me wash my clothes and then pack them for me.

702
00:49:15,360 --> 00:49:19,513
Are you not staying here?

703
00:49:19,513 --> 00:49:22,300
Do as I say.

704
00:49:22,300 --> 00:49:24,040
Okay.

705
00:49:31,260 --> 00:49:33,460
Aren't you going to live at home?

706
00:49:33,460 --> 00:49:36,013
Your father will be worried about you.

707
00:49:37,500 --> 00:49:41,853
It's none of your business whether I live at home or not.

708
00:49:41,853 --> 00:49:44,740
But this is your home.

709
00:49:44,740 --> 00:49:47,580
Are you sure this is my home?

710
00:49:47,580 --> 00:49:49,089
I'm sure.

711
00:49:49,089 --> 00:49:50,380
This is your home.

712
00:49:50,380 --> 00:49:53,660
Your dad's home. Your family's home.

713
00:49:53,660 --> 00:49:58,020
As long as you're still here, this is not my home.

714
00:49:58,020 --> 00:50:00,780
Because you're not my family.

715
00:50:00,780 --> 00:50:05,840
Can you give me a chance to be a part of your family?

716
00:50:05,840 --> 00:50:10,177
I can't. I won't let you be happy in this house.

717
00:50:10,177 --> 00:50:14,000
Khun Hom, the reason why I beg you

718
00:50:14,000 --> 00:50:17,200
is not to make myself happy

719
00:50:17,200 --> 00:50:20,780
but to make your dad happy.

720
00:50:20,780 --> 00:50:24,190
You made a scene and said that Kanghan and I

721
00:50:24,190 --> 00:50:26,760
stole your dad's love for you.

722
00:50:26,760 --> 00:50:30,660
Please think carefully about what you're doing now.

723
00:50:30,660 --> 00:50:32,980
Is it right?

724
00:50:32,980 --> 00:50:35,177
Look at me now.

725
00:50:35,177 --> 00:50:38,400
There is no home to return to, and I was removed.

726
00:50:38,400 --> 00:50:41,940
Doesn't that prove that I'm right?

727
00:50:41,940 --> 00:50:45,896
I'll hold you accountable for everything you do.

728
00:50:45,896 --> 00:50:49,280
I will remove you as the head of the Marketing Department.

729
00:50:49,280 --> 00:50:52,620
I want you to admit your mistake and apologize to Kanghan.

730
00:50:52,620 --> 00:50:56,000
No way. I won't apologize to her.

731
00:50:56,000 --> 00:50:59,780
I won't force you if you don't want to.

732
00:50:59,780 --> 00:51:02,420
I want you to make your own choices.

733
00:51:17,180 --> 00:51:20,900
You may not be right occasionally.

734
00:51:20,900 --> 00:51:23,640
Since you abandoned your dad,

735
00:51:23,640 --> 00:51:28,620
he will give his love to me and Kanghan.

736
00:51:28,620 --> 00:51:33,620
If he gives his property to us,

737
00:51:33,620 --> 00:51:36,020
don't blame me and Kanghan.

738
00:51:36,020 --> 00:51:38,880
You should blame yourself for it.

739
00:51:41,660 --> 00:51:43,900
Your clothes are packed.

740
00:51:43,900 --> 00:51:46,138
Do you want me to put them in your car?

741
00:51:46,138 --> 00:51:49,260
No. Take them to my room.

742
00:51:49,260 --> 00:51:51,100
I will live at home.

743
00:51:55,160 --> 00:51:57,900
Let's go, Khun Hom.

744
00:52:06,980 --> 00:52:11,940
Are you coming back to work after only a few days off?

745
00:52:11,940 --> 00:52:15,540
Actually, I'm not in good shape. But I'll think nonsense if I don't work.

746
00:52:15,540 --> 00:52:17,860
So I decided to come to work.

747
00:52:17,860 --> 00:52:19,643
Maybe I'll get over it faster.

748
00:52:19,643 --> 00:52:25,200
Besides, I would rather not trouble Khun Kheetika to take my place.

749
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:26,920
No worries.

750
00:52:26,920 --> 00:52:28,960
It's good that you've come back to work sooner.

751
00:52:28,960 --> 00:52:34,200
Maybe you can get a new girlfriend at the company.

752
00:52:37,560 --> 00:52:39,440
Will it be me?

753
00:52:39,440 --> 00:52:41,640
It's best if I were a monk.

754
00:52:43,600 --> 00:52:45,560
Awesome.

755
00:52:45,560 --> 00:52:47,100
Your face looks like a cow.

756
00:52:47,100 --> 00:52:49,620
- Are you saying I look like a cow?
- I'm not.

757
00:52:49,620 --> 00:52:53,120
But you have two horns like a cow.

758
00:52:53,120 --> 00:52:55,280
You can't find a boyfriend because you're mean.

759
00:52:55,280 --> 00:52:58,700
You got dumped. It's better that you've never had a girlfriend.

760
00:52:58,700 --> 00:53:02,240
Sādhu, I hope that your dream comes true.

761
00:53:02,240 --> 00:53:03,840
A relationship always starts with a fight.

762
00:53:03,840 --> 00:53:06,120
They will fall in love later.

763
00:53:06,780 --> 00:53:08,320
- It's impossible.
- It's impossible.

764
00:53:08,320 --> 00:53:09,780
[Mom]

765
00:53:09,780 --> 00:53:12,300
Really?

766
00:53:16,760 --> 00:53:18,800
Kanghan.

767
00:53:20,826 --> 00:53:23,360
- Hello.
- Hello, Mom.

768
00:53:23,360 --> 00:53:26,792
This is the green curry.

769
00:53:28,655 --> 00:53:31,360
Thank you. I'll go first.

